# The Gradle wrapper jar is committed on purpose: it is what makes `./gradlew` work on
# a fresh clone without Gradle installed. Must come after *.jar (last match wins), and
# needs the leading **/ to reach into each service's build rather than only the root.
!**/gradle/wrapper/gradle-wrapper.jar

